<p>I am developing one website using html5 and css3. There is one modal popup in one of my page. It consists of few divisions for displaying terms and condition text. I used next and previous jQuery function to slide those all divs.</p>  <p>The problem what I am facing is first time when I open the modal popup it is working fine but when I open it again without refreshing page, the if loop inside the jQuery is getting called twice and because of that alternate divs are getting visible.</p>  <p>I am sharing jQuery code and the modal popup code.</p>  <p>This is my jQuery</p>  <pre><code>$(document).ready(function(){     $("#divs div").each(function(e) {         if (e != 0){             $(this).hide();         }         if(e==0){             $(this).show();         }     });     $("#next").click(function(){         if ($("#divs div:visible").next().length != 0){    // &lt; This is the statement             $("#divs div:visible").next().show();          //   I am referring to             $("#divs div:visible").prev().hide();         }         else {             $("#divs div:visible").hide();             $("#divs div:first").show();         }      });     $("#prev").click(function(){         if ($("#divs div:visible").prev().length != 0){             $("#divs div:visible").prev().show().next().hide();     }         else {             $("#divs div:visible").hide();             $("#divs div:last").show();         }      }); }); </code></pre>  <p>Here is my modal popup div</p>  <pre class="lang-html prettyprint-override"><code>&lt;div id="terms" class="modal fade" data-keyboard="false" data-backdrop="static"&gt;   &lt;div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"&gt;     &lt;div class="col-md-"&gt;       &lt;div class="carousel-v1"&gt;         &lt;div id="divs"&gt;           &lt;div style="padding:20px;background:white;width:80%;margin-left:80px;"&gt;`&lt;/div&gt;           &lt;div class="" style="padding:20px;background:white;width:80%;margin-left:80px;"&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;           &lt;div class="" style="padding:20px;background:white;width:80%;margin-left:80px;"&gt;           &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;div class="carousel-arrow"&gt;           &lt;a class="left" id="prev"&gt;             &lt;i class="fa fa-angle-left"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;           &lt;/a&gt;           &lt;a class="right" id="next"&gt;             &lt;i class="fa fa-angle-right"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;           &lt;/a&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>